# Spark Social - Project Overview

This is a Flutter application for a social media platform inspired by TikTok, integrated with the Bluesky/AT Protocol.

## Main Entry Points
- [lib/main.dart](mdc:lib/main.dart) - Main application entry point
- [lib/src/sprk_app.dart](mdc:lib/src/sprk_app.dart) - Main MaterialApp configuration
- [pubspec.yaml](mdc:pubspec.yaml) - Project dependencies and configuration

## Key Architecture Files
- [lib/src/core/di/service_locator.dart](mdc:lib/src/core/di/service_locator.dart) - Dependency injection setup
- [lib/src/core/routing/app_router.dart](mdc:lib/src/core/routing/app_router.dart) - AutoRoute configuration
- [lib/src/core/storage/preferences/storage_manager.dart](mdc:lib/src/core/storage/preferences/storage_manager.dart) - Storage management
- [lib/src/core/utils/logging/](mdc:lib/src/core/utils/logging) - Logging framework

## Current Features
- **Authentication** (`lib/src/features/auth/`) - User login/logout with AT Protocol
- **Feed** (`lib/src/features/feed/`) - Main social media feed with posts and videos
- **Profile** (`lib/src/features/profile/`) - User profiles and profile management
- **Comments** (`lib/src/features/comments/`) - Comment system for posts
- **Search** (`lib/src/features/search/`) - Search functionality
- **Messages** (`lib/src/features/messages/`) - Direct messaging
- **Settings** (`lib/src/features/settings/`) - App settings and preferences
- **Home** (`lib/src/features/home/`) - Home navigation
- **Splash** (`lib/src/features/splash/`) - App initialization screen

